data.description:
What a deal!!! 5 bedroom home with lots of space!  
NO HOMES BEHIND- lots of privacy and open views.
Entire downstairs has new waterproof laminate flooring.  Kitchen has lots of NEW updates such as- granite counters, stainless steel appliances, farm sink, garbage disposal and faucet .Master bathroom has a new custom tiled shower. New toilets at master and guest bathroom. Nicely maintained grassy backyard.  Room for a pool! Copper Basin has a community pool included in the HOA dues.
